{"tid":864503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵大故障  港鐵 : 黃昏會再壊","createTime":"2018-10-16T08:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T09:18:33.000Z","uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"178c8248d48f6c26efc1bbd4a4a4a9a38c994842","tid":864503,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"劉天成指，荃灣線昨晚(15日)做更新系統測試，至於此項更新工作與今次四線信號故障有否關係，則需詳細調查，而為何兩個中央控制中心未能傳送指令亦在調查範圍內，他又辯稱每晚港鐵都做更新工作。<br />\n<br />\n被問及今次事故要近6小時才能大致完成復修是否太慢，劉解釋，信號系統由中央控制，並在車站區間有電腦運作，當港鐵人員發現系統出問題後，需逐一跟進各線合共20多個區間電腦，逐一重置恢復自動操作服務。<br />\n<br />\n劉指，列車服務現正執行非繁忙時間表，即約每4分鐘一班車，工程人員仍密切留意情況，他目前最關心能否應付黃昏繁忙時間加密班次至每2、3分鐘一班車，工程部門會繼續加強工作，並找出事故原因，他亦會與工程人員商討及部署，或會在稍後時間再向傳媒交代最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181016/s00001/cb2758f2c5a37326f49c6389f16e51f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181016%2Fs00001%2Fcb2758f2c5a37326f49c6389f16e51f6.jpg&h=443dbf96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b57fdaf2d961d5290aa2fbe747b1b8643d679f6","tid":864503,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a9dc224c0f280c0d02e7a5b9d2afe8cbc4f7c0","tid":864503,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"撚有講過會再壞？<br />\non99"},{"pid":"5f3730efbee3d0f1e46b6b9ad2ef7b6c75f65cf2","tid":864503,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53db5f90511eff44769f12ad4b9199f676a0d844","tid":864503,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as